{"lastModified":1764175819611,"uri":"c::21836669044::vessel::857d4e20-436e-11ef-b6c2-c9927170c278","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Summer/Winter Operating Area: Bahamas, United States of America- Florida East Coast, United States of America- Florida West Coast\n\nThis 78' Ferretti motor yacht epitomizes luxury, Italian craftsmanship, and seaworthy elegance, designed for discerning yacht enthusiasts who appreciate both style and performance on the water. The yacht has had a major refit in 2023 making her one of the nicest 78 Ferretti's on the charter market.\n\nExternally, the 78' Ferretti boasts a striking and aerodynamic profile, with sleek lines and a deep-V hull design that ensures stability and smooth cruising in various sea conditions. The yacht's exterior spaces are expansive and meticulously finished, featuring teak decking throughout, spacious decks for lounging and dining, and a flybridge that offers panoramic views and additional entertainment areas.\n\nInside, the 78' Ferretti showcases a blend of contemporary design and timeless elegance. The main salon is spacious and beautifully appointed, featuring high-quality materials such as fine woods, luxurious fabrics, and polished finishes. Large windows flood the interior with natural light, enhancing the sense of openness and connection to the sea.\n\nAccommodations aboard the 78' Ferretti are luxurious and comfortable, comprising Four staterooms with en-suite bathrooms to ensure privacy and convenience for guests. The master suite is a highlight, offering a spacious retreat with a king-size bed, ample storage, and sophisticated amenities. Guest cabins are equally well-appointed, providing plush accommodations for family and friends.\n\nThe yacht is equipped with state-of-the-art technology and amenities to enhance the onboard experience. This includes advanced navigation systems, entertainment systems, and a fully equipped galley where gourmet meals can be prepared by the onboard chef. The layout is designed to cater to both relaxation and entertainment, making it ideal for extended cruising or hosting intimate gatherings.\n\nIn terms of performance, the 78' Ferretti is powered by powerful engines that deliver impressive speed and efficiency, ensuring a smooth and exhilarating ride on the open water. The yacht is designed for long-range cruising capabilities, allowing guests to explore distant shores in comfort and style.\n\nOverall, the 78' Ferretti motor yacht is a testament to Italian craftsmanship and luxury, offering a combination of elegance, comfort, and performance that sets it apart in the world of yachting. It provides a sophisticated and memorable yachting experience for those who seek the ultimate in maritime luxury and adventure.","blueprint":{"name":"TWE11VE","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::857d4e20-436e-11ef-b6c2-c9927170c278::assets::1d1a3d60-8d7e-11f0-bd8e-5550877256eb/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::857d4e20-436e-11ef-b6c2-c9927170c278::assets::1d1b27c0-8d7e-11f0-bd8e-5550877256eb/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::857d4e20-436e-11ef-b6c2-c9927170c278::assets::1d1c3930-8d7e-11f0-bd8e-5550877256eb/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::857d4e20-436e-11ef-b6c2-c9927170c278::assets::1d102b40-8d7e-11f0-bd8e-5550877256eb/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::857d4e20-436e-11ef-b6c2-c9927170c278::assets::1d1f4670-8d7e-11f0-bd8e-5550877256eb/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::857d4e20-436e-11ef-b6c2-c9927170c278::assets::1d158270-8d7e-11f0-bd8e-5550877256eb/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::857d4e20-436e-11ef-b6c2-c9927170c278::assets::1d149810-8d7e-11f0-bd8e-5550877256eb/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::857d4e20-436e-11ef-b6c2-c9927170c278::assets::1d181a80-8d7e-11f0-bd8e-5550877256eb/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::857d4e20-436e-11ef-b6c2-c9927170c278::assets::1d131170-8d7e-11f0-bd8e-5550877256eb/{imageVariant}","/media/media::